</div>

</section><section class="page-section ">
  <div class="container">
     <div class="col9">
          <div class="content-block">
        <div class="page-content" data-id="50cec185aaba453b81a28941db76dc2e">
            <h3>H: Summary of who to contact for further information (last updated 7 May)</h3>
<p>A list of key CCFF contacts is provided below:</p>
<h4>General questions</h4>
<p>
If you wish to discuss the application process, your eligibility or need any more information about your options if you do not have a relevant public credit rating(s), then please contact the team at <a href="mailto:CCFF-Applications@bankofengland.co.uk">CCFF-Applications@bankofengland.co.uk</a>.</p>
<h4>Information for banks acting on behalf of companies</h4>
<p>If you wish to offer commercial paper, in either the primary or secondary market, you can complete the <a href="/-/media/boe/files/markets/covid-corporate-financing-facility/ccff-transaction-form.xlsx?la=en&amp;hash=B46C5A80DEB4C889BE2366F77B2F9DD2BA79D3D1" target="_blank" title="Opens in a new window">CCFF transaction form</a> and send to <a href="mailto:CCFFtransactions@bankofengland.co.uk">CCFFtransactions@bankofengland.co.uk</a>.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

